description: Recently sold: $275,000. Lake home for sale on Oak Lake. 100 feet of shoreline on this 400+ acre lake that has great fishing! Located near state land and off of State Hwy 23 makes this a nice hunting, 4 wheeling and fishing area. Lake home was custom built in 2001 with quality construction showing through! Enjoy for four seasons or use on weekends- either way you will not be disappointed with the features and space!Walk into the main level with cedar vaulted ceilings in the kitchen, dining and sitting room with built- in gas fireplace in the corner. Just off here is the 4 season cedar tong and groove room facing lakeside- currently the TV room. Walk out to upper deck from here. Spacious kitchen with ample cupboards and separate pantry. Master bedroom features private full bath. Additional bedroom and laundry room combined with 1/2 bath on this level.Lower level has large family room area with built in gas fireplace~ this leads out to the lower deck from here. Both decks have a thick glass insert for beautiful views of the lake. Bedroom and full bath with whirlpool can be found on this level along with ample storage and mechanicals. Great feature on this level is a tuck under garage used currently for mower and supplies needed for yard- making this an access from lakeside.Detached 3 car garage by driveway for ample room! Come and see today what we have to offer in this beautiful lake home at a great price!MLS #4592982, Pine County, Minnesota.DIRECTIONS:  Hwy 23 E at exit #195- up 18 mi to Co Rd 47. L 2.5 mi to Shady Oak Ln. R to property. Sign is up (90100 Shady Oak Lane, Kerrick, MN 55756).Please call Natalie at 612-390-3945 or 218-485-0229 for more information.
